➜好声音回归，直球导师李宇春鲨我！
http://www.sohu.com/a/414388091_255135	21143
<p>昨晚，<strong>音乐评论节目的王者《中国好声音》</strong>回归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/7c562e0726ca46b499ddc59402c54636.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>节目还没开播，先被硬核宣传笑死。<strong>李宇春李荣浩</strong>导师，这是要结盟了还是？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/28063553fac84a45aaa6c047ed3a2110.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/6be881318d33481abede21102dc9511e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
